            "<b>C.</b> <p>\\(R \\cap S = ( R \\cup S) - [(R-S) \\cap (S-R)]\\)</p>",
            "<b>D.</b> <p>\\(R \\cap S = ( R \\cup S) \\cup (R-S)\\)</p>"
          ],
          "correct_answer": "<b>A.</b> <p>\\(R \\cap S = ( R \\cup S) - [(R-S) \\cup (S-R)]\\)</p>",
          "marks": 1,
          "negative_marks": 0.33,
